# Bringing AI to the Classroom


#### Welcome! This professional learning module is designed to help you learn how to bring AI to the students in your classroom.

<img src="https://images.code.org/1cd0ec71458414495502b9598efd2028-image-1639773441510.37.01 PM.png" alt="Image of AI bot" style="border-radius:40px; float: right; padding-right: 75px; height: 275px; clear: both; margin: 0 0px 0px 0;">

## In this module, you will:

* #### Critically evaluate AI tools and resources for their applicability and effectiveness in the classroom.
* #### AI implementation strategies through the lens of Universal Design for Learning and Culturally Responsive Teaching.
* #### Explore how you could introduce and integrate AI technologies into your own classroom settings, taking into consideration your specific educational contexts and student needs.
* #### Learn about the resources available to teach about AI in your classroom.

